The paper uses the alternating direction method of multiplier (ADMM), which is a popular method in the field of distributed computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper discusses numerical examples to demonstrate the effectiveness of the proposed method, which falls under the category of simulation and modeling (cs.SI).
